<p>英 /ˌæbsənt'maɪndɪd/    美 /ˌæbsənt'maɪndɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-forgetful">1.★ <strong>心不在焉的；健忘的 (forgetful)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Grandpa’s been getting rather absent-minded lately. 
爷爷最近变得很健忘。</p></div></div>